<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') %>
<% locals.showBackBtn = true; %>

  <style>
    .legal-page {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .legal-page h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .legal-page .legal-meta {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
      padding-left: 0.75rem;
    }

    .legal-section p,
    .legal-section li {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .legal-section ul {
      padding-left: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .legal-divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--bg-tertiary);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .legal-nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .legal-nav a {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .legal-nav a:hover,
    .legal-nav a.active {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>

  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: January 2025 &middot; Effective immediately</p>


    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>1. About Rentlyst</h2>
      <p>Rentlyst is an online marketplace that connects buyers, sellers, renters, and service providers. We provide a
        platform ("the Platform") to facilitate listings and communications between users. <strong>Rentlyst is a
          mediator only</strong> — we are not a party to any transaction that occurs between users.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>2. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using the Platform, you confirm that you are at least 18 years of age and agree to be bound by
        these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use Rentlyst.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>3. Rentlyst's Role — We Are a Marketplace Only</h2>
      <p>Rentlyst provides a window — a digital space where listings are posted and users connect. We do
        <strong>not</strong>:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Own, manufacture, inspect, or verify any listed item, vehicle, property, or service</li>
        <li>Guarantee the quality, safety, legality, or accuracy of any listing</li>
        <li>Participate in or supervise any transaction, handover, or payment</li>
        <li>Intervene in or mediate disputes between users after a transaction occurs</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All transactions are solely between the buyer and seller/host. Rentlyst bears no liability for any loss,
        damage, injury, or dispute arising from a transaction conducted through the Platform.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>4. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>You are solely responsible for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The accuracy and legality of your listings and the items/services you offer</li>
        <li>Verifying the identity of the other party before meeting or transacting</li>
        <li>Exercising personal judgment and care during any exchange</li>
        <li>Complying with all applicable local, national, and international laws</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>5. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
      <p>You agree not to post listings for illegal items, engage in fraud or impersonation, harass other users, or
        attempt to circumvent the Platform's systems. Rentlyst reserves the right to remove listings or suspend accounts
        that violate these rules.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, Rentlyst, its directors, employees, and agents shall not be liable for
        any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your use of the Platform,
        including but not limited to financial loss, property damage, or personal injury arising from any listing or
        transaction.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>7. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We may revise these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Platform after changes are posted constitutes your
        acceptance of the new Terms. Please review this page periodically.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms? Visit our <a href="/help" class="legal-link">Help Center</a> to get in touch with
        the Rentlyst team.</p>
    </div>
  </div>